ient role); implementors should coordinate the 403 response path.\",\n          \"relation_hint\": \"see_also\",\n          \"target_section_id\": \"docs/spec/auth.md#0004-authorization\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"search_keys\": [\n        \"csrf protection\",\n        \"cross site request forgery\",\n        \"state changing requests\",\n        \"forbidden without token\",\n        \"request token validation\",\n        \"write action protection\",\n        \"unsafe method defense\",\n        \"Authentication Specification\",\n        \"CSRF Protection\"\n      ],\n      \"semantic_hash\": \"c1a6a4c9aec98c2168df8ababb237a8a89fec69eece9f46a7a884e24841cdbc5\",\n      \"source_document_id\": \"docs/spec/auth.md\",\n      \"source_hash\": \"02a54aadfea72152048dd1c09d1bf1e94ca9317da00e63d704f71a8252137356\",\n      \"source_section_id\": \"docs/spec/auth.md#0003-csrf-protection\",\n      \"source_span\": {\n        \"end_line\": 10,\n        \"end_offset\": 288,\n        \"start_line\": 7,\n        \"start_offset\": 175\n      },\n      \"stable_chunk_uid\": \"ead5b4571ab9f4d3\",\n      \"stable_section_uid\": \"ead5b4571ab9f4d3\",\n      \"summary\": \"Requires protection against cross-site request forgery for state-changing requests and rejects requests missing a valid token with a forbidden response.\",\n      \"text\": \"Authentication Specification / CSRF Protection | Requires protection against cross-site request forgery for state-changing requests and rejects requests missing a valid token with a forbidden response. | csrf protection cross site request forgery state changing requests forbidden without token request token validation write action protection unsafe method defense Authentication Specification | CSRF POST PUT PATCH DELETE\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"warnings\": []\n}","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8ec58f15-3081-4aed-bfdc-e5a2feb0380b","uuid":"36a5c1a2-d01c-4169-a2cb-773b9236f004","timestamp":"2026-05-22T16:09:43.936Z","tool_