{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01NpfLdnZ8MexsZ8gxJcVko2","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the information I need to construct the constraints JSON and the human-readable output.\n\nLet me analyze what I found:\n\n**Task**: Extract constraints to follow regarding authentication session expiration and CSRF.\n\n**From Source Specs (`docs/spec/auth.md`)**:\n\n1. **Session Management** (`#0002-session-management`):\n   - Login成功時: HttpOnly かつ Secure な session cookie を発行する\n   - 通常の session 有効期限は 30 分\n   - logout 時には即時失効する\n\n2. **CSRF Protection** (`#0003-csrf-protection`):\n   - State-changing requests (POST, PUT, PATCH, DELETE) require CSRF token validation\n   - Requests without a valid CSRF token are rejected with a 403 response\n\n**From Core Concept**:\n- Authentication centers on session cookies\n- CSRF protection applies to state-changing requests\n- Source Specs are the authoritative reference, not search results\n\n**From Purpose**:\n- Maintain the rationale behind authentication specifications before implementation and responses, ensuring session, CSRF, and permission constraints are verifiable\n\nNow I'm consolidating the specific constraints: session expiration at 30 minutes, HttpOnly and Secure flags on session cookies, immediate session invalidation on logout, CSRF token requirements for state-changing requests, and 403 responses for missing or failed token validation.\n\nWriting constraint JSON... I'm reviewing the session management requirements, including the 30-minute default timeout and immediate invalidation on logout, along with the CSRF token mandate for state-changing HTTP methods like POST, PUT, PATCH, and DELETE. Formatting the requirements documentation...","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":451,"cache_read_input_tokens":32033,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":451},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8ec58f15-3081-4aed-bfdc-e5a2feb0380b","uuid":"eeb155a9-1eca-4b6b-ba60-8e4ef1169352","request_id":"req_011CbHu4XNZ23x4irG4vjM3P"}
